13e0fed1d1219e6862c6409a95e629aebade9ce","tid":1647270,"uid":323879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:45:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n小編好俾心機！"},{"pid":"c7502d0cfa691c48a6e8519528e45658cc32eb4a","tid":1647270,"uid":237142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:54:58.000Z","msg":"好有Heart既搞手<br />\n推啊"},{"pid":"b025549170a659649ef26b164c6c8b87abff66f2","tid":1647270,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:02:11.000Z","msg":"推呀!!!"},{"pid":"2a50ec1e8ab028b0d8066403cc4c668c2192b0f8","tid":1647270,"uid":101991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:02:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18c467961924a32aac2c965e54871b196410b0de","tid":1647270,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:05:53.000Z","msg":"你改依個標題都幾難上到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8588dbce585dc7e05211f51beab58bda6fc25713","tid":1647270,"uid":296618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:06:22.000Z","msg":"行動post 推"},{"pid":"7ab61b2b30becfc88facacc3339da85c45cc3acf","tid":1647270,"uid":68298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:15:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"662477afc59bf63afe02399bb2b59c10945ff7e9","tid":1647270,"uid":19711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:19:16.000Z","msg":"p 牌照推。<br />\n日日做緊 已無搭狗鐵，食咩都check 左黃店先。<br />\n<br />\n但真心近日太多活動又太短宣傳，好撚亂。我等連登仔都未必跟得切。<br />\n星期六尖咀都幾單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，個個星期weekend, weekday 都參加戶外活動 有益身心。<br />\n唔撚覺支力，唔撚洗休息。<br />\n但麻煩攪手們有多d focus 同焦點。<br />\n真係有心參加都唔知點參。<br />\n講真，人力有限，不應用來鳩浪費。唔係一味出出出出啦咁就叫做左野，9 做有時仲衰過唔做。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太漫無目的，就算手足個人真係出左來，其實都無咩凝聚力。<br />\n人在心不在。運動真係會慢慢散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如，鳩叫行動而家已好少人參加。咁底成本，到底點撚解<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔專業建議，周末兩日一單（最多至兩單）大野，<br />\n加18 區。<br />\n平日三，五，或二四活動。裝飾連儂牆。<br />\n逢周三，黃店爆買。<br />\n逢周星，電影會，<br />\n大家加返hashtag, 好記又持續到落去。<br />\n之類之類。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有focus, 又唔太累。<br />\n<br />\n不割，唔完美可改善。多謝admin.<br />\n一齊討論，集思廣益。香港人再進化。"},{"pid":"3727ac89adadead474b4812159520ae91d2327ae","tid":1647270,"uid":298093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:13:12.000Z","msg":"大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e016d1b3a8a3fcca957b20c20a515c88d8c8f65","tid":1647270,"uid":261345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:58:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"840b791a39dd316e3ea40cc40cdac7718b68306f","tid":1647270,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T23:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌原罪"},{"pid":"db473b651581d0bbe638bd24081457be4e69c4cf","tid":1647270,"uid":279214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T23:26:09.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"282191fe1ea5bd20e399dc8549c501100a8813ef","tid":1647270,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:33:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b15a2e1417c55e63a6368ea395d08cd12c601599","tid":1647270,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8aa1c9692221dc60f2e41d97faff88e0e3bcef5","tid":1647270,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0